# 🎣 Fisch Macro Ultimate

> A powerful automation tool built to streamline your fishing gameplay and remove repetitive grind.

---

## 🌊 Overview

Fisch Macro Ultimate enhances your fishing experience by intelligently handling repetitive actions for you.  
It’s designed to improve efficiency, consistency, and overall earnings while keeping full customization in your hands.

Whether you're a casual player saving time or a dedicated grinder optimizing every catch, the macro adapts to your playstyle.

---

## ⚙️ Features

### 🎯 Automated Casting
Performs optimized fishing patterns to maintain high catch efficiency and consistency.

### 🧠 Smart Detection
Accurately detects catch moments with precise timing for improved success rates.

### 🛠️ Customizable Settings
Adjust behavior, timing, and patterns to match your personal playstyle.

### ⚡ Lightweight Performance
Built to stay fast and efficient without slowing down your system.

---

## 🚀 Why Use It?

- Reduces repetitive grinding
- Improves farming efficiency
- Fully adjustable to your setup
- Runs smoothly in the background

---

## 📌 Notes

Designed for users who want more control over their gameplay efficiency without sacrificing performance or stability.
